Reno Omokri, the popular Nigerian Public Commentator and Human Rights Activist has given tips on how one can use his/her phone to do outside calls to make money online.
Omokri who took to his social media page to share this said if one wants to make money, one will need to create value and that when one creates value, one will be rewarded.
Going further on the importance of using the Internet to make money, he said with internet, one will not be limited by space or time. This means you can work any time and reach more people. He concluded by saying people should use their “phone to blow”
His post read, “Making money is about creating value. You create value and get rewarded. And the Internet allows you to create value without the limitations of space and time. Start a YouTube channel. Become an affiliate marketer. Publish on Amazon KDP. Use your phone to blow!”


